    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">這根光滑的灰色木棒上刻著無數的符文。該法杖有</span><span class=\"1\">10</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">充能，每天黎明重新獲得[[/r 1d6+4]]充能。如果你用完最後一發充能，骰一個</span><span class=\"1\">d20</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">。若骰出</span><span class=\"1\">1</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">，則這根法杖變為灰塵，被摧毀了。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">當你持杖時，你可以使用一個動作，消耗</span><span class=\"1\">2</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">或更多的充能，來施放下列的法術之一，使用你的法術豁免</span><span class=\"1\">DC</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">和法術攻擊加成：@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.QD0hMadacCVoJGkn]{命運寵兒fortune』s favor}</span><span class=\"1\">(2</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">次</span><span class=\"1\">)</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">，@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.ZGvthYJNmIv8sDqj]{脈衝波動pulse wave}</span><span class=\"1\">(3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">次</span><span class=\"1\">)</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">，@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.c4Rwx5li2TEEQPzf]{引力裂溝gravity sinkhole}</span><span class=\"1\">(4</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">次</span><span class=\"1\">)</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">當你持有該杖時，若一個只針對你的咒語豁免失敗，你可以把此次失敗的豁免改為成功。這個屬性直到第二天黎明不能再次使用。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></div>",
